text: Hamilton County is a county in the U.S. state of Indiana. As of the 2020 census, the county's population was 347,467. The county seat is Noblesville. ==Cities== *Carmel *Fishers *Noblesville *Westfield ==Towns== *Arcadia *Atlanta *Cicero *Sheridan ==References== Category:Indiana counties Category:1823 establishments in Indiana
